edu.harvard.integer.service.discovery.snmp

Class SnmpServiceElementDiscover

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.service.discovery.snmp.SnmpServiceElementDiscover
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElementDiscoveryBase
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContainmentServiceElementWorker, HostMibServiceElementDiscovery, ParentChildServiceElementDiscovery

    public abstract class SnmpServiceElementDiscover
extends java.lang.Object
implements ElementDiscoveryBase
    The SnmpServiceElementDiscover is the base class for all SNMP service element discover. It provides some basic methods used on SNMP service element discovery. In order to kick off a discover for a network SNMP device, it needs to call the abstract method "discover". The output of the method "discover" a service element associated with network SNMP device.
